{"tid":1210744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登幫起底呢個PK黑警","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T14:22:08.000Z","uid":254159,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"37b0dac7ec3b12a5b8ce2b7020f9ec46f058c4f3","tid":1210744,"uid":254159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:22:08.000Z","msg":"【#BF社會熱話 反逃犯條例示威】警方向示威者發射布袋彈及橡膠子彈，網傳指有年輕人頭部中槍。<br />\n<br />\n下午三時示威者與警方爆發衝突，現場傳出三聲槍聲，警方後承認曾使用布袋彈及橡膠子彈，而亦有網傳照片示威者頭部中彈倒地。報道指，頭部受傷者是香港電台外判司機，現失去知覺，情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n根據過往指引，警方規定只能向下肢發射，以減低傷害程度。有人權組織權威人士指，假如示威者被布袋彈及橡膠彈射中，可導致骨折，嚴重可致命。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：網上圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/64333784_1380436555445600_8836642272306003968_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=821f3efbcecc249e0aaeac2f87a9b817&amp;oe=5D8CA0CB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F64333784_1380436555445600_8836642272306003968_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D821f3efbcecc249e0aaeac2f87a9b817%26oe%3D5D8CA0CB&h=0f7f41dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62360394_1380436505445605_706119660281528320_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=c755d294f361a32dc853776460d68911&amp;oe=5D92AC62\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62360394_1380436505445605_706119660281528320_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Dc755d294f361a32dc853776460d68911%26oe%3D5D92AC62&h=6eee3cf1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}